  <title>给照片和视频添加特效</title>

  <p>您可以给您的图片和视频添加滑稽、有趣的效果：</p>

  <steps>
    <item>
      <p>Click <gui style="button">Effects</gui>.</p>
    </item>
    <item>
      <p>Select the effect you want to use by clicking one of the options or
      select <gui>No Effect</gui> if you don't want to use one.</p>
    </item>
  </steps>

  <p><app>Cheese</app> offers 35 effects, of which only 9 are shown on the
  first page. Click the back and forward arrows next to
  <gui style="button">Effects</gui> to navigate to the other pages.</p>

